    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in showroom condition, appearing as if it just rolled off the assembly line. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory luster with a mirror-like finish, free of any stone chips, swirls, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of luxury; the premium leather seats show zero signs of wear, the original floor mats are pristine, and that distinct 'new car' scent lingers. Every button, dial, and electronic feature functions with precision. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, having been strictly garage-kept and serviced exclusively at authorized dealerships. We have the complete service history, all original keys, and the original window sticker available. This is not just a used car; it is a collector-grade investment for the discerning enthusiast who demands perfection. No accidents, no smokers, and no stories\u2014just pure, unadulterated quality.",
      "price": 43500.0,
